==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term/t|ang|swāpan}}. Cognate with Early Mod. West Frisian {{term|swiepe||whip, cleanse, sweep|lang=fy}}, from Old Frisian {{term|swēpa|lang=ofs}}, {{term|suepa||sweep|lang=ofs}}. see also {{term|swoop|lang=en}}.

