===Verb===
{{en-verb|sweeps|sweeping|swept}}

# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To [[clean]] (a surface) by means of a [[stroke#Verb|stroking]] motion of a [[broom]] or [[brush]].
# {{context|intransitive|lang=en}} To move through an ([[horizontal]]) [[arc]] or similar long stroke.
